# ⚔️ KanjiForge

[![Go Version](https://img.shields.io/badge/Go-1.21+-00ADD8?style=flat&logo=go)](https://go.dev/)
[![Ollama](https://img.shields.io/badge/Ollama-0.1+-green?style=flat&logo=ollama)](https://ollama.com)
[![License](https://img.shields.io/badge/License-MIT-blue.svg)](LICENSE)

**Forge kanji mastery with AI-crafted JLPT-style quizzes. 100% local, privacy-focused, and completely free.**

KanjiForge is a web application that uses local LLMs (via Ollama) to automatically generate Japanese JLPT-style multiple-choice questions from your kanji vocabulary data. No cloud API costs, no data leaving your machine.

